---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About" 
  description="About Nahlawi Tools - Free, privacy-focused online utilities that work entirely in your browser."
>
  <div class="tool-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="tool-container about-container">
        <header class="tool-header">
          <h1>About Nahlawi Tools</h1>
          <p>Free online utilities that respect your privacy</p>
		  <p><strong>Version:</strong> 3.0.0 - Built with Astro and Vue 3</p>
          <p><strong>Updated:</strong> December 2025</p>
        </header>

        <div class="tool-interface">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            Nahlawi Tools provides a collection of free, easy-to-use online utilities that solve everyday problems. 
            We believe that useful tools should be accessible to everyone without compromising privacy or requiring registration.
          </p>

          <h2 class="section-heading">Why We're Different</h2>
          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <span class="feature-icon">üîí</span>
              <h3>100% Private</h3>
              <p>All processing happens in your browser</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <span class="feature-icon">üö´</span>
              <h3>No Tracking</h3>
              <p>No cookies, no analytics, no ads</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <span class="feature-icon">‚ö°</span>
              <h3>Lightning Fast</h3>
              <p>Instant results with no server delays</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <span class="feature-icon">üíª</span>
              <h3>Works Offline</h3>
              <p>Use tools even without internet</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <span class="feature-icon">üì±</span>
              <h3>Mobile Friendly</h3>
              <p>Optimized for all devices</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <span class="feature-icon">üÜì</span>
              <h3>Forever Free</h3>
              <p>No premium plans or paywalls</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="section-heading">Our Principles</h2>
          <ul class="principles-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Privacy First:</strong> Your data never leaves your device. 
              All tools run entirely in your browser using client-side JavaScript.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>No Registration Required:</strong> Use all tools immediately 
              without creating an account or providing any personal information.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Open and Transparent:</strong> Our code is clean, 
              well-documented, and available for review.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Accessibility:</strong> We strive to make our tools 
              accessible to everyone, regardless of ability or device.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> We regularly add new tools 
              and improve existing ones based on user needs.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="section-heading">Technology Stack</h2>
          <p>
            Nahlawi Tools is built with modern web technologies:
          </p>
          <ul class="tech-list">
            <li>Astro + Vue 3 for optimal performance</li>
            <li>TypeScript for type safety and better development experience</li>
            <li>Responsive design that works on all devices</li>
            <li>Progressive Web App capabilities for offline use</li>
            <li>Minimal external dependencies for better privacy and performance</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="section-heading">Feedback & Suggestions</h2>
          <p>
            Have an idea for a new tool? Found a bug? We'd love to hear from you! 
            Your feedback helps us make Nahlawi Tools better for everyone.
          </p>
          <div class="feedback-actions">
            <a href="https://github.com/rnahlawi/tools-nahlawi" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              üìù Submit Feedback on GitHub
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box coming-soon">
          <h3>üåü Always Improving</h3>
          <p>We're constantly working on new features and tools. Our toolkit now includes:</p>
          <div class="tools-summary">
            <div class="summary-column">
              <h4>‚úÖ Calculators</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Age Calculator</li>
                <li>Percentage Calculator</li>
                <li>BMI Calculator</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-column">
              <h4>‚úÖ Text Tools</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Word Counter</li>
                <li>Case Converter</li>
                <li>Text Reverser</li>
                <li>Remove Line Breaks</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-column">
              <h4>‚úÖ Generators</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Password Generator</li>
                <li>Random Number</li>
                <li>Lorem Ipsum</li>
                <li>QR Code Generator</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-column">
              <h4>‚úÖ Developer Tools</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Base64 Encoder</li>
                <li>URL Encoder</li>
                <li>Hash Generator</li>
                <li>JSON Formatter</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .section-heading {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .principles-list {
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .principles-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .principles-list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .tech-list {
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .tech-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .feedback-actions {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .coming-soon {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .tools-summary {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .summary-column h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  }

  .summary-column ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .summary-column li {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
  }

  .summary-column li::before {
    content: "‚Ä¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .tools-summary {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>